# Excludes build/runtime cruft from the Docker context. Source dirs (parts, seeds, data,
# catalog, registry, blueprints, tests, docs, scripts, lessons) are KEPT: the API image
# (Dockerfile.api) serves a self-audit surface that reads them, so it copies the whole repo.
# The gateway image (Dockerfile) uses explicit COPYs, so it is unaffected by what is kept.
.git/
.github/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.hypothesis/
.coverage
coverage.xml
codeforge.db
save.json
characters.json
accounts.json
*.kdbx
security-evidence/
reports/
site/
casts/
node_modules/
.next/
.env
e2e/
